Commentary Text: Chahal to de Kock, out Bowled!! 50th scalp for Chahal at the Chinnaswamy. Told ya! He's RCB's trumpcard and straightaway gets his team the breakthrough. CDG will be a relieved man for sure. Poor shot from de Kock, especially having tried this off the first ball of the over. Spinning into him and the Southpaw went for the fancy reverse after taking his front foot forward. Was in no position to play that shot and gets an under-edge which deflects back onto the stumps. The home crowd goes bonkers as RCB pick up their first wicket. de Kock b Chahal 23(20) [4s-2 6s-1]
